These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, sprite
Nationality: egyptian, polish
Job: accountant, engineer
Movie-Genre: documentary, sports
Flower: azalea, sunflower
Birthday: august, july
Transport: bus, taxi
1. Nationality:polish is on the left of Transport:bus##1
2. Birthday:july is in an odd position##4
3. Beverage:sprite is on the left of Job:accountant##1
4. Movie-Genre:sports is on the left of Flower:azalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality         | polish  | egyptian       |
| Job           | engineer   | accountant    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | documentary   |
| Flower   | sunflower      | azalea     |
| Birthday         | july | august      |
| Transport     | taxi       | bus           |

